tool_description:
This API is a simple ROgue Company API made with info found online on different resources.
It started as a personal project, but given that there seems to be no official API, I decided to make a fan based one and make it public.
title: RoCO API

api_list.name: Get All Weapons
api_list.description:
Returns list of all weapons in the DB. If filters are sent, results will be filtered.
Available filters are: "id", "name", "description", "class", "rogues"
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://roco-api.p.rapidapi.com/weapons"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "roco-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

body.name: Trench
body.bio: The heart of the Rogue Company team, Trench was personally recruited by The Director early on in its formation to help guide the group’s moral compass. A natural leader and cool under pressure, Trench is well respected by all member of Rogue Company.

active.name: Barbed Wire Grenade
active.description: Create a field of barbed wire that damages and slows enemies

body.name: Anvil
body.bio: Veteran of a hundred battles, Anvil brings stability and security to any mission. He has seen it all. He finds success on the battlefield by being more heavily armed and heavily armored than anyone else in the fight. Anvil was one of the first recruited to Rogue Company.

active.name: Barricade
active.description: Deploy a barricade that blocks damage and movement. Activate again to break the glass and create medium cover.

passive.name: Immune
passive.description: Gain immunity from disorient and blind effects.
